data.description: Welcome to 6124 Bowline Lane! This end unit 3 bed 2.5 bath was built in 2019. As you enter you notice the spacious open living with wood floors that connects to the dining space and an open kitchen with granite counters and stainless steel appliances. There is a half bath with an updated vanity just off the living room. Past the kitchen is a huge 1st floor primary suite, with trey ceiling, a custom walk in closet and dual vanity in the bathroom. Head upstairs and see you a nice loft area that would make a great gaming space. There is a second full bath with dual vanity in the hallway upstairs and two comfortable bedrooms. Outside you have a privacy fenced yard with a detached 1 cart garage. The home feels practically brand new!
